is going to be a big one!

257
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:55,802
- For next time, what do you say?
- "I have an extra ticket."

258
00:18:56,052 --> 00:19:00,807
"An extra ticket."
Not "two tickets".

259
00:19:01,683 --> 00:19:06,855
The first time you asked a guy out
